| Field             | Description                                                    |
| ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `hex_id`          | Unique national hexagon identifier                             |
| `english_name`    | Species common name                                            |
| `scientific_name` | Scientific name                                                |
| `season`          | Season represented by the abundance estimate                   |
| `ebird_category`  | eBird abundance category                                       |
| `bam_category`    | BAM abundance category                                         |
| `date_range`      | Species-specific breeding-season window used for BAM summaries |
| `n_surveys`       | Number of BAM surveys within date window                       |
| `n_detections`    | Number of BAM surveys detecting the species                    |

